<br>
Burning Woods:<br>
There are 2 spawn spots that pop Nezekezena and Phurzon, named wurms. Now having done this part for mage epic I reailze how hard it can be, but the fun and rewards make it VERY good to do for everyone! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
1) massive MASSIVE amount of mobs. You need abut 4+ groups and you pull every darn thing around, sometimes using AOE, mahaha! Folks report its the most xp they have ever earned up to about lvl 56, and the PH and named mobs are blue to lvl 60s by way. And there's no fighting over spawns!<br>
<br>
2) named mobs drop nice items. Gullerback the gorilla (forget the shoudlers/arms drops). nezekezena and especially Phurzon drop Wurm Scale Cloak shoulder item 0.0 weight AC10 MR10 Fr20 Uber dragon/monk/resist item. From an 8 hour camp we got 4 of the cloaks.<br>
<br>
3) Epics. Slixin Klex, Nezekezena and Phurzon drop mage epic items. And the 2 wurms drop bard epic items. Note the bard item drops a lot, the mage items you may get 2 or 3 in a LONG raid.<br>
<br>
4) Spells can drop from random mobs, thought that's rare its still nice.<br>
<br>
I know the exact spawn point of the east/mid wurm point, not the north/West one.<br>
  <br>
  To do this you must go to the EXACT point, then kill EVERY mob in a large radius to you kill the wandering PH,. Sometimes you're in luck and nez/Phurz are up. You MUST do this on spawn point, 3 minute respawn, and nezekezena can gate AND summon if she's lvl 51. very bad if she gates away and summons folk :&gt; the pullers, prefferably rangers or druids, need hp/magic resist buffs or they'l get blasted if pull the wizard wrums.<br>
<br>
 I'm willing to help with this, and wish nothing in return, I'll get wurm cloak another time, but would like to help mages out there get epic items, and others have some real good fun <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I'll go along to show spawn point and blast, it's such fun AOEing a pulled train <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
